               <p>Fifth Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Sergeant Arabin.</p>
               <p>350. 
               
                  <persName id="t18320105-57-defend648" type="defendantName">
                     BENJAMIN 
                     SMITH
                  <interp inst="t18320105-57-defend648" type="surname" value="SMITH"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320105-57-defend648" type="given" value="BENJAMIN"></interp>
